{
  "texts": [
    "In the literature, several examples of such XAR models have been proposed [2,8].2.1.2 Research question.",
    "Let 𝐻 be a set of 𝐾 different alternative XAR models ℎ 1, ℎ 2,..., ℎ 𝑘.",
    "Let 𝑃 be a pool of time window.",
    "Given a window 𝑤 ∈ 𝑃, all the XAR models in 𝐻 provide the same output activity but possibly different explanations.",
    "Our research question is the following: can we leverage Large Language Models (LLMs) to choose the best XAR model in 𝐻, given the explanations provided to the windows in 𝑃?"
  ]
}